1
00:00:10,655 --> 00:00:12,791
Good afternoon. Do you speak English?
下午好. 您说英语吗?

2
00:00:14,736 --> 00:00:15,357
Wonderful.
太好了.

3
00:00:15,819 --> 00:00:18,101
I'm calling from the United States.
我从美国打来.

4
00:00:18,620 --> 00:00:21,228
I'd like to speak with Milos Hermann, please.
我想和Milos Hermann讲话, please.

5
00:00:23,238 --> 00:00:23,701
Yes. Thank you.
Yes. 谢谢.

6
00:00:29,505 --> 00:00:29,916
Hello Milos!
你好, Milos!

7
00:00:30,792 --> 00:00:33,162
This is Anne Holland, from the Sheraton Boston.
我是Anne Holland, 来自波士顿的Sheraton.

8
00:00:36,511 --> 00:00:38,614
Yes, me too. How are you?
是的, 我也是. 你好吗?

9
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:41,873
I'm very well, thank you.
我很好, 谢谢.

10
00:00:44,146 --> 00:00:44,538
Excuse me?
Excuse me?

11
00:00:46,332 --> 00:00:48,178
No, I'm calling from Boston.
不是, 我是从波士顿打来的.

12
00:00:48,567 --> 00:00:50,662
We'll have our arrival dates very soon.
我们很快就会知道到达的日期了.

13
00:00:52,522 --> 00:00:58,383
Milos, I wonder if there's an interesting theatre or club we can go to while we're in Prague.
Milos, 我想知道在布拉格(Prague)有没有好的剧院或俱乐部,我们到那儿时可以去.

14
00:01:00,506 --> 00:01:01,864
We can? Excellent.
我们可以? 太好了!

15
00:01:04,460 --> 00:01:08,355
Good idea. We can lunch at the hotel restaurant by all means,
好主意. 我们完全可以在饭店的餐厅吃午饭,

16
00:01:08,846 --> 00:01:11,157
but then let's get into town for drinks and dinner.
然后去市中心喝酒和吃晚饭.

17
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,961
Milos, tell me, is there a hair salon at the hotel?
Milos, 告诉我,饭店里有美发厅吗?

18
00:01:22,536 --> 00:01:24,557
I see Hm.
我明白了. Hm.

19
00:01:26,003 --> 00:01:27,846
My hair doesn't travel very well.
旅行时我的发型总是保持不好.

20
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,609
Yeah, hat shop is a solution...
Yeah, 帽子是个解决的办法...

21
00:01:32,922 --> 00:01:34,606
No, I don't think a wig is necessary.
No, 我不认为有必要戴假发.

22
00:01:36,222 --> 00:01:36,762
OK then.
OK then.

23
00:01:38,604 --> 00:01:41,652
Yes. I look forward to it. Good bye.
Yes. 我很期待去那儿.  再见.

24
00:01:47,035 --> 00:01:47,991
Maybe I do need a wig.
也许我的确需要一顶假发

